import React from 'react'
import {FooterContainer, FooterSubHeading, FooterSubscription,
FooterSubText, Form, FormInput} from './Footer.elements'
import {Button} from '../../globalStyles'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <FooterContainer>
            <FooterSubscription>
                <FooterSubHeading>
                    wkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwkwk
                </FooterSubHeading>
                <FooterSubText>
                    wkwkwkwkwkwkwkwwk
                </FooterSubText>
                <Form>
                    <FormInput name="email" type="email" placeholder="Your Email" />
                        <Button fontBig>Subscribe</Button>
                </Form>
            </FooterSubscription>
            <FooterLinksContanier>
                <FooterLinksWrapper>
                    <FooterLinksItems>
                        <FooterLinkTitle>About</FooterLinkTitle>
                        <FooterLink to='/about'>How it works</FooterLink>
                        <FooterLink to='/'>TARAK</FooterLink>
                        <FooterLink to='/'>DUNG</FooterLink>
                        <FooterLink to='/'>CESS</FooterLink>
                        <FooterLink to='/'>DUAR</FooterLink>
                    </FooterLinksItems>
                </FooterLinksWrapper>
            </FooterLinksContanier>           
        </FooterContainer>
    )
}

export default Footer
